is_a

public boolean is_a(KisaoTerm term)
Boolean test for whether this term IS-A subtype of the term argument. If this.equals(term), this method returns true.
So, if term is the root term (KISAO:0000000), for any subtype, 
    anyterm.is_a(root_term) == true;

Parameters:
term - The KisaoTerm under test.
Returns:
true if this object IS-A term, false otherwise.
